---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — AI Smart Tools"
  description="Our privacy practices: what data we collect, how we use it, and your rights."
>
  <article class="container-prose py-12 md:py-16 prose-custom">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <p class="lead">
      AI Smart Tools respects your privacy. This page explains what data we collect and how we use it.
    </p>
    
    <h2>1. Data we collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Server logs</strong>: standard request metadata (IP, user agent, page requested) for 30 days, to operate and secure the site.</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics</strong>: anonymized, aggregate analytics via Plausible.io (no personal data, no cookies, no cross-site tracking).</li>
      <li><strong>Email</strong>: if you subscribe to our newsletter, your email address. We never sell it.</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>2. Affiliate links</h2>
    <p>
      Clicking an affiliate link may set a cookie in your browser so the vendor can attribute the referral. 
      AI Smart Tools does not have access to this cookie.
    </p>
    
    <h2>3. Your rights</h2>
    <p>
      You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of any data we hold about you by emailing <a href="mailto:privacy@aismarttools.com">privacy@aismarttools.com</a>.
    </p>
    
    <h2>4. Children</h2>
    <p>
      This site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children.
    </p>
    
    <h2>5. Contact</h2>
    <p>Data controller: AI Smart Tools. Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@aismarttools.com">privacy@aismarttools.com</a>.</p>
    
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-8">Last updated: July 19, 2026.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
